snippet.textDisplay: This song features 2 people's loving conversations, will break all the records, I believe. Almost all songs usually praise the ladies, here the lad. Wow! What an excellent tune of Mr. Shiblu Mredha but Ms. Aleya Begum's magical voice topped all. Salute all including the great musicians and Mr. Emon Chowdhury for bringing us this masterpiece composition.
